lead_paragraph: Tom Jenkins was eight under par through 16 holes in the second round of the Commerce Bank Championship in East Meadow, N.Y., when play was suspended for the day after a third rain delay. Jenkins was 10 under for the tournament and had a one-stroke lead over Tom Wargo, who was five under for the round through 12 holes.
